WEBVTT

08:21.375 --> 08:24.962
The wool and cashmere blend
that you like. Milled in England.

08:25.713 --> 08:27.381
This fabric
will last forever.

08:27.465 --> 08:30.301
Beautiful.
You really outdid yourself.

08:31.302 --> 08:32.678
How much do I owe you?

08:32.762 --> 08:35.056
Don't insult me.
After you helped my nephew?

08:35.139 --> 08:38.935
You pay for material only.
As long as my eyesight holds up.

08:39.018 --> 08:42.438
Thank you. This is
for your staff, for putting up with you.

08:43.481 --> 08:46.442
I'll put the suits
in garment bags.
